<p>I like this watch so much. So today I tried to rebuild it using Javascript and CSS3. Wish you like it. Pure CSS and no jQuery required. <em>Itâ€™s not advertisement</em>, So I didnâ€™t put any logo in to this demo. Thank you!</p>

<p>Using javascript to move 3 pointer and indicate the current date. Using CSS3 to make the appear right under different browers.</p>

